rply in favour in the 1970s and has since remained perennially popular."],"variants":[]},{"name":"of","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["Short form of   Oswald   or any of the various other names beginning with <i>Os-</i>."],"variants":[]},{"name":"Yorkshire","type":"LAST","attribution":"Dictionary of Family Names in Britain and Ireland © University of the West of England 2016","meanings":["English: locative name from the county of Yorkshire."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Emma of Yorkshire was born about 1148, in Yorkshire East Riding, England, United Kingdom as the daughter of Walden de Teisa. She married Ralph FitzRalph de Grimthorpe about 1145, in Grimesthorpe, Yorkshire, England. They were the parents of at least 1 son. She died about 1185, at the age of 39."},"et":{"Abt 1148–Abt 1185":"umbes 1148–umbes 1185","1148–1185":"1148–1185","1100–1197":"1100–1197","1165–1219":"1165–1219","–Male":"Surnud","Abt 1185":"umbes 1185","before 1158":"enne 1158","1148":"1148","Abt 1165":"umbes 1165","1100":"1100","1165":"1165","1197":"1197","Abt 1148":"umbes 1148","1185":"1185","1219":"1219","Givendale, East Riding of Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire East Riding, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Grimthorpe, Pocklington, East Riding, Yorkshire, England":"Pocklington, Yorkshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1148–Abt 1185":"noin 1148–noin 1185","1148–1185":"1148–1185","1100–1197":"1100–1197","1165–1219":"1165–1219","–Male":"Kuollut","Abt 1185":"noin 1185","before 1158":"ennen vuotta 1158","1148":"1148","Abt 1165":"noin 1165","1100":"1100","1165":"1165","1197":"1197","Abt 1148":"noin 1148","1185":"1185","1219":"1219","Givendale, East Riding of Yorkshire, England":"Yorkshire East Riding, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Grimthorpe, Pocklington, East Riding, Yorkshire, England":"Pocklington, Yorkshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1148–Abt 1185":"environ 1148–environ 118